parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various issues, including stalling, loss of power, and malfunctioning of essential systems, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The dashboard lights flash
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission malfunctions
the battery drains
and the vehicle experiences electrical burning smells.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the battery to drain, leading to stalling, loss of power, and malfunctioning of essential systems, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery drains
the vehicle stalls
the alternator fails
and the electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The center stack screen is unresponsive
the language changes to German
the Bluetooth is not working
and the audio system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the transmission can cause loss of control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The transmission malfunctions
the vehicle stalls
and the transmission automatically parks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the anti-theft system can cause the vehicle to stall or become difficult to start, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The anti-theft system malfunctions
the vehicle stalls
and the vehicle is difficult to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the windows and trunk can cause inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The passenger side window is stuck
the trunk does not open
and the window and trunk release buttons do not function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of a crash or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting gears
the transmission slips or hesitates when accelerating
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Power train failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of a crash or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Clutch failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of a crash or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failure can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, increasing the risk of a crash or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's systems malfunction
the dashboard warning lights illuminate
the vehicle's electrical components fail to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, increasing the risk of a crash.
symptoms: The vehicle's brakes fail to function properly
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or death to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
airbags fail to deploy in a crash
delayed deployment of airbags
or the airbag warning light comes on and off intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause the airbag to rupture, sending shrapnel into the passenger compartment, increasing the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the dealership refuses to repair the vehicle under recall
or the parts for the recall repair are not available.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating a potential problem with the airbag system, which can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag sensor is faulty
or the airbag warning light comes on and off intermittently.
